1. Info
2. Installation
3. Starting
4. Themes
5. Plugins
----------------------------------------------------------------

1. System config and info written in Ruby. Project is available on Github - Sysconfig-ruby.
----------------------------------------------------------------

2. I tested it on:
  * Ruby 1.8.7 with Mongrel 1.1.5
  
I recommend Ruby 1.8.7 : )
----------------------------------------------------------------

3. If you have ruby and mongrel now, you should only run script:
  ruby sysconfig.rb Template_name Port Host
example:
  ruby sysconfig.rb 1234 default 0.0.0.0

But if you run script without arguments, it also will work!
Default port: 1234
Default theme: default
Default host: 0.0.0.0
----------------------------------------------------------------

4. If you want (Yes, you want) more themes, you can find them on github - search sysconfig-ruby-themes ; ]
----------------------------------------------------------------

5. Oops. Not implemented yet.
